title: Out of Their Element
text: While this objective is undamaged, increase the cost of each non-neutral out-of-faction card by 1.

title: Luke's Speeder Bike
text:
Edge (1).
Reaction: After you lose an edge battle, remove this unit from the engagement.

title: Ambush Point
text:
Enhance your play area.
Limited.
Each out-of-faction non-fate card in an edge stack loses 1 Force icon during the edge battle.

title: Force Persuasion
text: Action: Place 1 focus token on a target Character or Creature unit. If it is an out-of-faction unit, place 2 focus tokens on it instead.

title: Secret Weapons
text: While this objective is undamaged, [Smugglers and Spies] Vehicle units you control cannot be targeted by enemy card effects.

title: Tydirium
text:
Edge (X). X is the number of enemy units participating in this engagement.
Interrupt: When this unit is destroyed, decrease the Death Star dial by 1 (to a minimum of 0).

title: Stolen Speeder Bike
text: Reaction: After this unit is focused to strike as an attacker, instead of resolving its combat icons, place 1 focus token on the engaged objective. (Limit once per phase.)

title: Stolen AT-ST
text: While this unit is ready, it cannot be affected by enemy combat icons.

title: Hiding Among Enemies
text: Action: Place 1 shield on a target [Smugglers and Spies] Vehicle unit. Then, discard 1 card at random from an opponent's hand.

title: Target of Opportunity
text: If you are the attacking player, deal 1 damage to the engaged objective.

title: Courage of the Tribe
text:
Limit 1 per objective deck.
Reaction: After you refresh, remove 1 focus token from a target Ewok unit.

title: Chief Chirpa
text:
Each other friendly Ewok unit gains +1 damage capacity.
Reaction: After a phase begins, focus an Ewok unit to draw 1 card.

title: Ewok Horde
text: Reduce the cost of this unit by 1 (to a minimum of 3) for each Ewok unit you control.

title: Ewok Horde
text: Reduce the cost of this unit by 1 (to a minimum of 3) for each Ewok unit you control.

title: Bright Tree Village
text:
Enhance your play area.
Each Ewok unit you control or in your edge stack gains 1 Force icon.

title: Battle of Endor
text: For this edge battle, this card gains +1 Force icon (to a maximum of +3) for each Endor objective or enhancement in play.

title: Merciless Plans
text: Reaction: After a mission enters or leaves play, set the Balance of the Force to the dark side.

title: Boc
text:
Elite.
This unit gains [Blast Damage] [Blast Damage] and targeted strike while participating in an engagement against a mission.

title: Expendable Scout
text: Action: Sacrifice this unit to have a player choose and discard 1 card from his hand. Then, that player draws 1 card.

title: Sith Lightsaber
text:
Enhance a Force User or Force Sensitive unit.
Enhanced unit gains [Unit Damage] [Edge-enabled Tactics].

title: Secret Objective
text: If you are the attacking player, you may choose an enemy objective that you have not engaged this phase. If you do, you are now engaged with the chosen objective instead.

title: Dark Genocide
text: Reaction: After this mission is completed, name a Trait other than Character or Vehicle. Deal 66 damage to each enemy unit with that Trait.

title: Sector Lockdown
text: While this objective is undamaged, each player cannot play copies of unit cards that are in his discard pile.

title: Captain Zed
text:
Elite.
While this unit is ready, cards cannot leave your opponents' discard piles.

title: Stalker
text:
Shielding.
While this unit is attacking, it gains [Edge-Enabled Blast Damage] for each out-of-faction unit in the defending player’s discard pile.

title: Storm Commando
text:
Reaction: After this unit enters play, discard the top card of a target opponent's deck.
Interrupt: When this unit leaves play, discard the top card of a target opponent's deck.

title: Sector Garrison
text:
Enhance your play area.
Limited.
Action: Focus this enhancement to shuffle a unit from your discard pile back into your deck.

title: Search and Detain
text: Action: Look at the top 3 cards of an opponent's deck. Discard 1 of those cards, place 1 on the bottom of its owner's deck, and return the remaining card to the top of its owner's deck.

title: The Spice Trade
text:
Limit 1 per objective deck. Elite.
Forced Interrupt: When this objective is destroyed, remove it from the game instead of placing it in the light side victory pile.

title: Moruth Doole
text: Reaction: After an objective is destroyed, move 1 focus token from a unit you control to a target enemy unit.

title: Energy Spider
text:
No enhancements.
This unit does not refresh during the refresh phase.

title: Energy Spider
text:
No enhancements.
This unit does not refresh during the refresh phase.

title: Spice Blitz
text: Action: Remove all focus tokens from a target unit. If that unit is still in play at the end of the phase, place twice that many focus tokens on it.

title: Hallucination
text: You may resolve the effects of a fate card not named Hallucination in any edge stack as if it were revealed in your edge stack. If the Balance of the Force is with the dark side, resolve the effects twice instead.
